<Title>Main Landing Gear Axle Remote Data Concentrator</Title>
<DispatchCondition>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>One per truck may be missing provided connector cover dispatch equipment
K32036 is installed on the wire bundle plug. For the axle remote data concentrator
missing, the associated antiskid control, the brake temperature monitoring, and tire
pressure indication systems must be considered inoperative.</Para>
<Note>
<Para>The airplane must be dispatched using MEL items 32-42-02, 32-46-01 and 32-49-01</Para>
</Note>
<Note>
<Para>Associated axle RDC magnetic ring/flux link may be broken or missing.</Para>
</Note>
